---
---

<section class="section" id="about" data-reveal>
  <div class="container narrow">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <span class="eyebrow">// about</span>
      <h2>Builder. Second year.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid" style="display: grid; gap: 4rem; grid-template-columns: 1fr;">

      <div class="about-copy">
        <p>
          I'm a second-year AI student at UET Lahore. I write a lot of Python, some <span style="white-space: nowrap;">C++</span>, and more time in the terminal than I'd like to admit. I got into this because I wanted to understand how things actually work.
        </p>

        <p>
          Not the theory in isolation, but what happens when you run it on real data, with real constraints, on a machine that has better things to do. That's still what pulls me toward NLP pipelines and low-level tooling.
        </p>

        <p>
          Outside that I'm into Linux, FOSS, animal welfare, and cats. I think the most interesting software is written by people who care about something other than software.
        </p>

        <div class="skills-grid" aria-label="Skills">
          <div class="skill-group">
            <span class="skill-label">Core</span>
            <div class="skill-pills">
              <span class="skill-pill">Python</span>
              <span class="skill-pill">C++</span>
              <span class="skill-pill">Linux</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill-group">
            <span class="skill-label">ML & Data</span>
            <div class="skill-pills">
              <span class="skill-pill">PyTorch</span>
              <span class="skill-pill">scikit-learn</span>
              <span class="skill-pill">spaCy</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-list">
        <article class="timeline-item primary">
          <div>
            <div class="timeline-year">2024 — Present</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>BS Artificial Intelligence, UET</h3>
            <p>Focused on machine learning architecture, systems programming, and applied mathematics.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div>
            <div class="timeline-year">Current Focus</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Systems & Infrastructure</h3>
            <p>Building the infrastructure layer beneath the models. Moving past standard model training to focus on data structures, Linux concepts, and low-latency implementation.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div>
            <div class="timeline-year">Current Rabbithole</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Hands-On Machine Learning</h3>
            <p>Reading Aurélien Géron.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-heading {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .about-copy {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-copy p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-group {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }

  .skill-label {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .skill-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-pill {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .timeline-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(9rem, 12rem) 1fr;
    padding: 1.5rem 0; /* Tightened from 2rem to create a denser log feel */
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: transparent;
  }

  .timeline-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--border);
    background: transparent;
    transform: none;
  }

  .timeline-item.primary {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: transparent;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .timeline-item p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .timeline-item h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .timeline-year {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .timeline-item.primary .timeline-year {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 699px) {
    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>